{"tid":360451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【自駕遊車禍】港人一家四口遊澳洲 失事撞橋兩死兩命危","createTime":"2017-08-15T10:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T02:44:51.000Z","uid":65328,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"86d60157e2157d1de02422e5b9442e3ec4654689","tid":360451,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:00:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170815&amp;guid=57084099&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170815%26guid%3D57084099%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=X3OJrcPTv%2BVtzxqpA7mgoP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=80444b21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170815%26guid%3D57084099%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=aecf45a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170815&amp;guid=57084099&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n一名47歲香港男護士，於本周日在澳洲新南威爾士州租用豐田Camry，載同妻兒及外母自駕遊，途經澳洲東岸一公路時失事撞向橋躉後翻滾墮坡，車禍中妻子及外母當場不治，事主和兒子則送往醫院搶救，情況危殆。當地警方表示已知會香港當局，並調查事件原因。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，重傷男子姓葉(47歲)，在本港任職護士，日前趁兒子放暑假，遂一家四口往澳洲旅遊，先抵達布里斯本機場，在昆士蘭省一帶展開旅程，曾遊覽當地國家公園等等。<br />\n<br />\n事發於當地周日下午4時40分，葉駕駛豐田Camry，載同46歲妻子、64歲外母及14歲兒子，離開Byron Bay後途經Clothiers Creek Road，駛至Pacific Highway時意外駛撞向橋躉及墮坡。"},{"pid":"9ff67a8cd8a915bec5151f0e1c4e2823dfc3431d","tid":360451,"uid":65328,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:07:04.000Z","msg":"老婆外母都死左"},{"pid":"01b9c7dbc9a06f6f35b30cd57693227632a0520d","tid":360451,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108fe625509a0f57a9fc4a4b6842b99dd2abd0b8","tid":360451,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:18:21.000Z","msg":"十一月會去Cairns同Melborune<br />\n會租車搾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed5e81752741ae9dd9a9ba04c89b7bf5287ec24","tid":360451,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"80ab6ea48e601feefa48594ebc10518b714c4728","tid":360451,"uid":46454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:38:35.000Z","msg":"有無澳洲巴絲打可以解釋下,點解係澳洲自駕遊ge意外率咁高? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0dff4f276b740e8f5cafe9c017fa8f12fe8e246","tid":360451,"uid":17103,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:20:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無澳洲巴絲打可以解釋下,點解係澳洲自駕遊ge意外率咁高? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為好多人中左 &quot;香港地路窄車多, 香港開得掂外國一定得&quot; 呢挺垃圾流言. 家上放假個人會放鬆戒備同好多闊長路會不自然加速.<br />\n<br />\n係外國開車係可以悶死你,一條路就係一條路. 單線 80 - 100. 一唔留心就可以突然駛離行車線.<br />\n<br />\n另外一樣係大霧大雨, 以前唔識死一霧見唔到前面得一片朦都照開 110 .. 我諗香港就真係無呢 D 極端裝況."},{"pid":"fd3e915adf0d940c0a5d46ce56b4c17d22efeeb5","tid":360451,"uid":44925,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:24:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無澳洲巴絲打可以解釋下,點解係澳洲自駕遊ge意外率咁高? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為好多人中左 &quot;香港地路窄車多, 香港開得掂外國一定得&quot; 呢挺垃圾流言. 家上放假個人會放鬆戒備同好多闊長路會不自然加速.<br />\n<br />\n係外國開車係可以悶死你,一條路就係一條路. 單線 80 - 100. 一唔留心就可以突然駛離行車線.<br />\n<br />\n另外一樣係大霧大雨, 以前唔識死一霧見唔到前面得一片朦都照開 110 .. 我諗香港就真係無呢 D 極端裝況.</blockquote><br />\nCity香港難揸啲<br />\n但highway其實外國難啲，啲車密麻麻但勁多車係起碼70mph+既情況下左穿右插，香港唔會有"},{"pid":"e9bf8e309aeaaa7cc1fba3a776f44eb95f3164bc","tid":360451,"uid":57962,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:26:28.000Z","msg":"