:360451,"uid":28277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:39:51.000Z","msg":"因為好易瞓著，個fd 果次就咁炒左，我坐隔離都來不及反應叫醒佢，同埋好易越渣越快，我果時不斷提醒自己唔可以超速"},{"pid":"63195145e56f24fe1e0aa6e185ce22db95b69cf3","tid":360451,"uid":21102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:41:57.000Z","msg":"RIP<br />\n醒返點面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce272a1360b42a7b8008f49efc107805de11dbcd","tid":360451,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:42:20.000Z","msg":"福氣"},{"pid":"fc23917f5b90de235255982c048ceb4ab2f9aef6","tid":360451,"uid":52826,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:42:26.000Z","msg":"你地外國渣過未架? 長途一定租架有speed limit既踩住咁去啦.咪防左越渣越快"},{"pid":"47136d7763bcb54e476685e40a0cdafe198c8f68","tid":360451,"uid":35420,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:43:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地外國渣過未架? 長途一定租架有speed limit既踩住咁去啦.咪防左越渣越快</blockquote><br />\n但冇防恰眼訓過隔離線"},{"pid":"61cd8d02804461edddc1aac04b80e3b3f71af85e","tid":360451,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:44:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你地外國渣過未架? 長途一定租架有speed limit既踩住咁去啦.咪防左越渣越快</blockquote><br />\n但冇防恰眼訓過隔離線</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551a79a6884ffaa0f386326e181986588a0e1be2","tid":360451,"uid":136735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你地外國渣過未架? 長途一定租架有speed limit既踩住咁去啦.咪防左越渣越快</blockquote><br />\n但冇防恰眼訓過隔離線</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n衝出黎柒"},{"pid":"87b51c67f67b497e724c50f3cdc68b304856a647","tid":360451,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:47:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4931ad485050238bf6c9f28681ac601e3