:"係美國試過sf揸落la 仲要夜晚7點先出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  臨到la前恰住上shoulder 好彩有轟轟聲同埋條女尖叫 如果唔係應該回唔到呢個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15684c8341117ed503dcc6a50378d6fb02d2577c","tid":360451,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4922d33f6464d183fd01eadca140a6838760d64","tid":360451,"uid":17425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無澳洲巴絲打可以解釋下,點解係澳洲自駕遊ge意外率咁高? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為好多人中左 &quot;香港地路窄車多, 香港開得掂外國一定得&quot; 呢挺垃圾流言. 家上放假個人會放鬆戒備同好多闊長路會不自然加速.<br />\n<br />\n係外國開車係可以悶死你,一條路就係一條路. 單線 80 - 100. 一唔留心就可以突然駛離行車線.<br />\n<br />\n另外一樣係大霧大雨, 以前唔識死一霧見唔到前面得一片朦都照開 110 .. 我諗香港就真係無呢 D 極端裝況.</blockquote><br />\nCity香港難揸啲<br />\n但highway其實外國難啲，啲車密麻麻但勁多車係起碼70mph+既情況下左穿右插，香港唔會有</blockquote><br />\n而且澳洲d公路太多突發情況，袋鼠，雀，羊啊牛啊都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n揸長途又易分神，見條大直路無車想快到目的地又會唔覺意超速，所以其實外國highway真係好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n曾經坐fd車係澳洲成架車炒到4輪朝天total lost, 好好彩車入面5個人都只不過係擦傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔覺意超速係個人自制能力不足，死左唔使恨"},{"pid":"463f0679e89d38cd35c44b1536bb4cdcead25e26","tid":360451,"uid":17425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:46:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為好易瞓著，個fd 果次就咁炒左，我坐隔離都來不及反應叫醒佢，同埋好易越渣越快，我果時不斷提醒自己唔可以超速</blockquote><br />\n其實呢個世界有樣野叫 cruise control"},{"pid":"ace8eb8537fe67a07e60932cdad89b3c705a0f2e","tid":360451,"uid":121517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T16:48:33.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c9ddfb9bfcc90c8221c29a8ab31e752069e1a0","tid":360451,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:41:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當年考完個牌第一次揸就係一年後係Tasmania揸左個幾星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係Perth揸左年幾 去到Tasmania揸都好鬼驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夜晚揸山路玩命真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n山路多灣只要你唔過快就冇事，大直路你先仆街。 幾百km 一條大直路真係好易眼訓。"},{"pid":"6e119973c4cd8ee79fc345b1051250449c986b91","tid":360451,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>英國撚試過連揸5個幾鐘，車住老婆仔女開到成190mph, 攰過連打3次丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n外國條路少車你唔覺自己揸到咁快，小小唔留神你已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我fd係英國揸開車,返到黎都揸得好快,成日屌其他司機揸得慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實有時快車會好o的， 高度集中。<br />\n反而大直路keep 110,120km/h 真係好惡頂。 有次開朋友架c36  飛到150mph都好似行緊60咁，架車太定好易訓著。"},{"pid":"9d247455ed95d3d7a824cc3f6d3b76e0376a375c","tid":360451,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T17:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bb545b73d22e24e9